{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1732326397.125578", "card_id": "Q_4762172524", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 197}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "湖南发现超 40 条金矿脉，储量超 1000 吨，价值达 6000 亿元，意味着什么？对经济有何影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "11 月 21 日，据新华社消息，湖南平江万古金矿田探矿获重大突破。湖南省地质院在地下 2000 米以上深度地层发现超 40 条金矿脉，金品位最高达 138 克 / 吨，探矿核心区探获黄金资源量 300.2 吨，地下 3000 米以上远景黄金储量超 1000 吨，以现行金价计算资源价值达 6000 亿元，对助力国家经济社会发展特别是资源安全保障具有重要意义。湖南发现超 40 条金矿脉：储量超 1000 吨 价值达 6000 亿元"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55e0d435a5ec7c72ff9eff186a0e9616_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "358 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4762172524"}}, "attached_info": "CkEImYrz4fG5sJ9nEAMaCTExMTkyOTA5NyDMrPy5BjAAOMAEQAByCjQ3NjIxNzI1MjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1732326397.126600", "card_id": "Q_4712311257", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 79}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待拳头官宣 S14 总决赛全球「观众峰值达到 5000 万」，除中国大陆地区外「观众峰值仅为 670 万」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "拳头官方宣布，2024LOL 全球总决赛冠亚军决赛 T1 对阵 BLG 的比赛包括中国大陆直播平台的全球观众峰值达到 5000 万。这一数据仅次于 S11 决赛的 7386 万。分均观众则达到 3300 万。而除中国大陆地区外观众峰值为 670 万。 4"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-99ef3f2a691d97f721fa0b67bbb7d39d_b.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "236 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B730