4 公里以上的里程区间，武汉地铁和成都地铁的划分更为细致，将它们进一步细分为三段收费。当里程超过 40 公里时，在同等地铁费用下，乘客在成都和武汉能够乘坐的里程数更多。记者综合对比几座城市地铁的优惠措施发现，虽然各大城市都推行多乘坐多优惠，但杭州的优惠力度最大，武汉地铁价格在不同消费金额段与其他城市相比有高有低。武汉地铁回应市民反映地铁票价贵：会向主管部门反映"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-118a469dec4d55507cf91ed29a8b0560_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "14 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4813238830"}}, "attached_info": "CkEImYrz4fG5sJ9nEAMaCTExMTkzOTI2OSDM8P+5BjAAOKAGQA1yCjQ4MTMyMzg4MzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1732326397.134282", "card_id": "Q_339984106", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "史书上有哪些让你动容的小人物？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c231325811543cf0506cbea5d188c463_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "13 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/339984106"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImYrz4fG5sJ9nEAMaCDM3ODI5MDUxIJG3wOoFMAA4jwFADnIJMzM5OTg0MTA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1732326397.134472", "card_id": "Q_351175902", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1921}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "当你看见有怀孕女士一个人单独出门的时候是什么感觉？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在街上，在医院，在餐馆——"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1d133edd3d69c2d42ec8284961941b01_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.2 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/351175902"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImYrz4fG5sJ9nEAMaCDQwMzE3MDA1IJDmoO0FMAA4kRNAD3IJMzUxMTc1OTAyeACqAQliaWxsYm